      <li><span>a CV of no more than two pages, in PDF format</span></li>
      <li><span>a portfolio of no more than three pages, including examples of recent work, in PDF format</span></li>
    </ul>
    <p>The closing deadline for applications is 30 April 2023 at 23:59.</p>
    <p>Please submit applications by email to info@climateart.org.uk</p>
